ing: 1 (14.5 ounce) carton Campbell'sÂ® Creamy Herb & Garlic with Chicken Stock Soup
1 (12 ounce) package frozen mixed vegetables (carrot, green beans, corn, peas), thawed
n: Quick Chicken Pot Pie from Campbell's Kitchen
des: "You can have a delicious pot pie on the table quickly and easily. A combination of cooked chicken, frozen veggies and creamy herb and garlic soup is topped with biscuit crust and baked to golden perfection. Give it a try, this is comfort food that's sure to become a family favorite!"
ins:
Heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Stir the soup, chicken and vegetables in a 9-inch deep-dish pie plate.
Stir the milk, egg and baking mix in a small bowl. Spread the batter over the chicken mixture.
Bake for 25 minutes or until the topping is golden brown.
